In a way , we are aliens to each other too. Aliens are a very wide category and an area we have barely any knowledge about ,,, however we can use this analogy to try and predict if they'll like our music or food . Just like how each human is distinct ,,, considering that each alien is different too, they all may have different preferences as well ,, our world being so vast ,,, and constantly developing in both the fields ,, I'm quite sure most aliens would find certain genre of music ,, a certain cuisine or a dish they connect too ,, it is although a hard conclusion to make whether it would be so ,, it is the closest we can assume given our understanding of them being limited
